title: Nike SB | Euro Series 2016 | Berlin Invite
description: Nike SB’s Denny Pham, Giorgi Balkhamishvili, Justin Sommer, Farid Ulrich and friend Linus Werner warm up and invite you to the fourth and final stop of the 2016 Nike SB European Contest Series, the Berlin Open, on July 8th - 10th at the Nike SB Shelter, Berlin.
